581
00:40:06,000 --> 00:40:08,800
You see. You really are able to talk well.

582
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:11,300
You were so blindly stubborn in the beginning.

583
00:40:13,600 --> 00:40:15,500
Holy Master,

584
00:40:15,500 --> 00:40:18,600
I have one more weapon that I'd like to show you.

